## CHANGELOG.md

All notable changes to this project are documented here.  
This changelog mirrors the commit history from GitHub.

# Changelog

## v1.0 – Initial Setup
- Created project using Expo TypeScript template
- Added splash screen with chef logo
- Added navigation logic for splash → home → payment

## v1.1 – Menu Management
- Implemented Add Dish feature (name, description, price, course)
- Added filtering for courses (Starter, Main, Dessert)
- Calculated total and average prices dynamically

## v1.2 – Payment and UI Enhancements
- Added Payment Summary screen
- Included “Record Payment” and “Back to Menu” options
- Improved button layout (Save & Cancel) and design consistency
- Changed background color and text styling for better contrast

## v1.3 – Final Submission Version
- Created a link to the git respository
- Completed README.md and Changelog documentation
- Tested successfully on Expo Go (TypeScript version)


